thread_conversation_history.body:
Hi there,

Following up on our conversation, here’s a proposal outlining how
ZemZen can help the Tilden Hotel enhance its online presence and drive
more direct bookings. We're excited about the opportunity to create a
stunning website that showcases your unique features and enhances the
guest experience.

As discussed, we have built a demo website to showcase what we can do
for your company. Please take a look:
https://6000-firebase-studio-1750647069045.cluster-aj77uug3sjd4iut4ev6a4jbtf2.cloudworkstations.dev/

I've attached the full proposal for your review, which details our
approach and the benefits you can expect. I'm confident that a new
website will significantly improve your brand image and revenue.

To keep things moving, let's schedule a quick meeting to discuss your
project in more detail. What time works for you?

Best regards,

Lexi
Sales
sales@zemzen.org
